channel.title: Final Judgement V3 - The Final Chapter
channel.description:
~I am officially closing Final Judgement~
Reason being: Ryley is quitting and to be honest he was one of the main reasons I wanted to actually restart Final Judgement. With actual competent programmers by my side we could had worked together to create a magnifient, bug FREE game. But with his resignation also comes mine I am afraid. I would like to just say thank you to everyone who has supported me on finishing the final chapter of Final Judgement.
if you wish to, you may start up Final Judgement and finish this dream that I was given but I am stepping down as well. Without Ryley by my side it just wouldn't be right nor would it feel right.
-Loveandpower -Co Owner of Final Judgement
p.s. I request this topic to stay open until the 18th thanks.
